title: Routledge Philosophers Series - Ten Volumes
description:
Ten volumes of the Routledge Philosophers series.  Each book provides a thorough, upd-to-date but accessible overview of the philosopher in question.  All are high quality pdf files.  

Includes volumes on Aristotle, Spinoza, Rawls, Merleau-Ponty, Darwin, Leibniz, Hegel, Schopenhauer, Kant and Husserl.  These are all I have access to -- if you have others, please upload them!

I just collected these files and put them together  Thanks to the original uploaders for making them accessible.  

This is only my second torrent -- please comment if you have any problems.  

And if you're new at using torrents, please remember to allow your files to seed until your ratio is higher than 1.0 after you finish a download.  It will allow others to continue having access to these files indefinitely.  Thanks and enjoy!
